data.description: Prime Location Alert!!! Nestled in the heart of Tallahassee, directly across from the renowned Tallahassee Nurseries, this one-story gem resides on a peaceful street with only six neighboring homes. The major upgrades have already been taken care of, boasting all-new windows valued at $10,000, a 2022 AC unit, and a freshly wired-in hot tub. The expansive concrete deck, a recent addition, offers a fantastic space for outdoor gatherings. Plus, the backyard has been adorned with over $10,000 worth of landscaping enhancements in recent years. The property is equipped with an irrigation system and regular services for yard maintenance, mosquito control, termite prevention, and yard mite management. A listing of this caliber is truly one of a kind! Don't miss out!
